  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kill thousands of Bugs in Entomophobia, a roguelite reverse-bullethell, gather exp from slain bugs to level up, and choose from 3 upgrade cards to try and build the craziest combo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932700/extras/d8351ce29880f97848e38a35fb9a566e.poster.avif?t=1729878443\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932700/extras/d8351ce29880f97848e38a35fb9a566e.webm?t=1729878443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932700/extras/d8351ce29880f97848e38a35fb9a566e.mp4?t=1729878443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Auto-firing weapons as well as a controllable gun.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect goop to gain experience, level up, and snowball to murder all the bugs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick 20 minute runs.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Kill Bugs, Level Up, Pick Upgrades, and Repeat.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932700/extras/baeda2167f290dd1931b1a6bce1b538c.poster.avif?t=1729878443\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932700/extras/baeda2167f290dd1931b1a6bce1b538c.webm?t=1729878443\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1932700/extras/baeda2167f290dd1931b1a6bce1b538c.mp4?t=1729878443\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Currently, the cards consist of weapon cards, some buff cards, and some infinitely stacking stat cards.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>PERMANENT UPGRADES:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Speed (up to 25% increase)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Max Health (up to 50% increase)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Health Regen (up to .5 per sec)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Stamina Regen (up to 1 per sec)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Max Stamina (up to +125 stamina)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Skips (up to 4)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Damage (+35% max)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Rerolls (up to 3)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Armor (-3 max)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Cooldowns (-6% max)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Gold Goblet (+50% shells)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Crit Damage (+105% max) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Please wishlist it helps out a lot.</h2>",
